text: Beata Syta (born 10 April 1971) is a Polish badminton player, born in Warsaw. She competed in women's doubles at the 1992 Summer Olympics in Barcelona. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Warsaw Category:Polish female badminton players Category:Olympic badminton players of Poland Category:Badminton players at the 1992 Summer Olympics
